snippet.title: GoobnBalloonsDX Announcement Trailer!
snippet.description:
Join Goobert, Bethany, Mr.Analogue, and the lovable bird Pajarito, in their mission to save the planet GoobStar from the invading balloon menace and stop the evil forces who are up to no good! 

GoobnBalloons DX comes out in summer 2023 on Steam! Wishlist TODAY!
